Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.51,0:00:30.00,Jinrui,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等好久了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.00,0:00:31.24,Jinrui,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
